<!-- Our Story Section -->
<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
                <div class="hero-image-placeholder" style="height: 400px;">
                    <i class="bi bi-building-fill"></i>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h2>Our Story</h2>
                <p>En Avant Physical Therapy was founded in 2009 by Dr. Sarah Mitchell with a simple but powerful vision: to create a place where every child could receive expert physical therapy in an environment that felt safe, welcoming, and even fun. The name "En Avant" - French for "Forward" - reflects our commitment to helping every child move forward in their development.</p>
                <p>After years of working in clinical settings, Dr. Mitchell saw firsthand how a child's progress could be dramatically improved when therapy felt less like work and more like play. She assembled a team of dedicated professionals who share her passion for pediatric care and her commitment to family-centered treatment.</p>
                <p>Today, En Avant has helped over 500 families in our community, and we continue to grow while maintaining the personal, attentive care that has always been at our core.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

